{"id": "1411879739853111327", "channel_id": "1411879739853111327", "type": 0, "author_id": "885882671899746305", "author_name": "cwz.io", "author_bot": false, "content": "我來賺點銀芯诶嘿\nID: 100698939\n\n首先是一些密契的風味文字，很多英文也有押韻喔\n\n### 【密契】機械降神\n\n齒輪的轟鳴，神明的降臨。\n鋼鐵的外衣，機械的表皮。\n冰冷的意志，眾生的低吟。\nThe roar of gears, the god unseen.\nA shell of steel, a skin machine.\nA will of frost, the mortals keen.\n\n### 【密契】扭曲雙子·白\n\n祂微笑，你沉陷。\n白色雙子贈你溫柔、予你安眠。\nIt smiles, you sink.\nThe White Twin grants you grace, and bids you rest.\n\n### 【密契】扭曲雙子·黑\n\n祂凝視，你湮滅。\n黑色雙子賜你力量、引你忘卻。\nIt gazes, you wane.\nThe Black Twin grants you power, but bids you forget.\n\n### 【密契】埋骨地絮語\n\n埋葬的不是骨，而是未竟的夢。\nBuried are not bones, but unfinished dreams.\n\n### 【密契】無垢啟示錄\n\n「神國永恆」\n它記載著某個國度的過去、現在與未來。\n\"The Realm endures\"\nIt records the past, present and future of a realm.\n\n### 【密契】海歸線\n\n一段傳說，一朵浪花；\n一名遊子，一紙約定。\nA tale told, a wave born;\na wanderer, a vow sworn.\n\n### 【密契】四月禮讚\n\n三月花開，張燈結彩\n四月花開，繁花似海\n五月花開，昔人不再\nMarch blooms, lanterns burn bright.\nApril blooms, a sea of blossoms white.\nMay blooms, yet the old have vanished from sight.\n\n〈釵頭鳳‧四月〉\n施粉黛，綰蕙蘭，去年巳月燈千盞。\n醉虹霓，艷江南，春色連空，競沒湖畔，漫！漫！漫！\n牡丹綻，芳心亂，今欲賞花花已殘。\n塵緣斷，君未返，悽愴悲惋，情思淚潸，嘆！嘆！嘆！\n\n---\n\n最後是一些自創刻印\n\n### 鍛造\n\n打出後選擇X張抽/棄牌堆的牌升級\n\n### 治癒\n\n打出後回復X點生命\n\n### 預備\n\n使附加的牌獲得保留、預備X\n\n### 抵抗\n\n打出後抵抗下X次獲得的負面效果", "timestamp": "2025-09-01T01:06:01.438000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-09-01T01:24:37.703000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 5}, {"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [{"id": "1411879740473741384", "filename": "Forging.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 8225, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1411879739853111327/1411879740473741384/Forging.png?ex=69fb3cb9&is=69f9eb39&hm=422a1d1480e45430c1728e47e963201a2546b18822898a5be5967307e0efa767&"}, {"id": "1411879740998160565", "filename": "Healing.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 9997, "url"